originalText.text: This "therapist" is terrible. He makes snap judgments, interrupts repeatedly and is deaf.  You have to repeat yourself multiple times or speak very loud in order to get your point across.  Even then he asks you a question about something that you just said as though you never said it, he seems very unfocused/uninterested in what you are actually saying.  IF you are looking for ACTUAL therapy, or any sort of help, DO NOT go to him!
